  "body": "## Issue\n\nWhen trying to customize the build, truffle ignores some entries. For instance:\n\n```\n build: {\n        \"index.html\": \"index.html\",\n        \"app.js\": [\n            \"javascripts/app.js\"\n        ],\n        \"app.css\": [\n            \"stylesheets/app.css\"\n        ],\n        \"images/\": \"images/\",\n        \"js/\": [\n            \"bower_components/jquery/dist\",\n            \"bower_components/bootstrap/dist\"            \n        ]\n    },\n```\n\nwill copy the content of `bower_components/jquery/dist` into `js/` as expected.\nHowever `bower_components/bootstrap/dist` is not copied.\n\nSwapping the entries:\n\n```\n build: {\n        \"index.html\": \"index.html\",\n        \"app.js\": [\n            \"javascripts/app.js\"\n        ],\n        \"app.css\": [\n            \"stylesheets/app.css\"\n        ],\n        \"images/\": \"images/\",\n        \"js/\": [\n            \"bower_components/bootstrap/dist\",\n             \"bower_components/jquery/dist\"            \n        ]\n    },\n```\n\nit is now `bower_components/bootstrap/dist` that is copied properly but the jquery files are not.\n",
